details: The 12th Generation Of Intel Core Processors Are Here! name: Silicon 16GB (8 X 2) 3200Mhz Gaming RAM
details: Silicon Power DDR4 UDIMM Is Compatible With The Intel Haswell-E Platform And X99 Series Motherboards Also Like The Intel Skylake Platform And 100 Series Motherboards. Silicon Power XPower Turbine 16GB 3200Mhz RAM Enables Higher Performance And Stability For Advanced Gamers, Multimedia Pros, And DIY Enthusiasts And Allows You To Experience Super-Fast Data Transfer Rates With 17GB/S Of Bandwidth, Which Is 33% Faster Than DDR3-1600.

name: Gigabyte AORUS M.2 1TB Gaming SSD
details: The World First PCIe 4.0x4 Controller, Phison PS5016-E16 Controller, Made By 28nm Manufacturing Technology. The Advanced Fabrication Process Ensures PS5016-E16 Has Enough Compute Power For ECC Processing When Adopting The Latest 3D TLC NAND Flash. PS5016-E16 Also Features Eight NAND Channels With 32 CE Targets, DDR4 DRAM Caching, And A PCIe 4.0x4 Interface. As For Features, The Chip Supports The NVMe 1.3 Protocol, LDPC Error Correction, And Wear Leveling, Over-Provision Technologies To Improve Reliability And Durability Of SSDs.
